v2_542bb975.description: Auto-generated translation for: FluentAI turns your everyday entertainment into effective language lessons. Instead of structured lessons, you learn naturally through content you enjoy. Our AI-powered system provides context-aware translations and explanations, making learning more engaging and effective.

Sistem kami yang dikuasakan oleh AI menyediakan terjemahan dan penjelasan yang peka terhadap konteks, menjadikan pembelajaran lebih menarik dan berkesan.

v2_1352eda1.description: Auto-generated translation for: What is FluentAI?

v2_548d3e48.description: Auto-generated translation for: FluentAI is a browser extension that helps you learn languages while watching videos. It automatically shows translations, explanations, and pronunciation guides for words and phrases in your target language as you watch content on platforms like YouTube, Netflix, Disney+, and Prime Video.
v2_548d3e48.message: FluentAI ialah sambungan pelayar yang membantu anda mempelajari bahasa sambil menonton video. v2_16a88605.description: Auto-generated translation for: Which languages are supported?

v2_092c62d4.description: Auto-generated translation for: FluentAI supports all languages through our AI-powered translation system. v2_092c62d4.message: FluentAI menyokong semua bahasa melalui sistem terjemahan berkuasa AI kami. Bahasa yang paling umum seperti Bahasa Inggeris, Sepanyol, Perancis, Jerman, dan sebagainya, biasanya mempunyai kualiti terjemahan yang paling tinggi.
